From: Pavel Moravec <pmoravec@redhat.com>
Date: Fri, 1 Feb 2019 09:19:56 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] [satellite] don't collect /root/ssl-build

Recursive listing of the directory is sufficient.

Resolves: #1555

Signed-off-by: Pavel Moravec <pmoravec@redhat.com>
---
 sos/plugins/satellite.py |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/sos/plugins/satellite.py b/sos/plugins/satellite.py
index 26dbc0e..c50c2ec 100644
--- a/sos/plugins/satellite.py
+++ b/sos/plugins/satellite.py
@@ -63,7 +63,7 @@ class Satellite(Plugin, RedHatPlugin):
             "/var/log/nocpulse/TSDBLocalQueue/TSDBLocalQueue.log"
         ])
 
-        self.add_copy_spec("/root/ssl-build")
+        self.add_cmd_output("ls -lanR /root/ssl-build")
         self.add_cmd_output("rhn-schema-version",
                             root_symlink="database-schema-version")
         self.add_cmd_output("rhn-charsets",
